title: Murals from the Hand Drawn Originals of Ilonka Karasz
description: Luxograph print of the artist's hand-drawn originals on linen. The titles include Trees, Sand Garden, East of the Sun, Serenade, Water Music, A Thousand and One Nights, Air-Fire-Water-Earth, Arches, The Closed Garden, Byzantine Curtains, Scene Chinoise I and II, Puppies and Bamboo in Moonlight, and The Pines of China.
